{
  "stem": "13483.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But they never tell you where.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "May-- April or May, 1944.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because we were put in sealed camps in England.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because there was such a lot going on in England-- I mean, I think you had to be there to really appreciate the enormity of the scheme, the plan.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But when you saw thousands and thousands of vehicles, tanks, guns, you know, being lined up all over some of the roads, the main roads, and especially in Southern England, you knew something was going on.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was thousands and thousands of American troops.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We did.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, like I was saying, there was a great big camp at the time, a really enormous, big camp.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, we were put into what we called sealed camps.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was, they put you there and you couldn't get out.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was just prior to D-Day.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Or a month or so before D-Day, they were all sealed.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And you were amongst American soldiers, part of the American Army.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So obviously, we knew what was happening.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We knew there was going to be an invasion, but where or when, we didn't know.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Like I shipped out from Harich the 3rd of June, which was three days before D-Day.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And all I remember is that most of the soldiers with me, we-- we went by LST, which was Land and Ship Tank.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And for three days, we really didn't know-- we knew we-- there was an invasion, but I think most of us were seasick at the time.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Fortunately, I wasn't, but most of them were.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was probably a good sailor.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But we had three pretty awful days in the English Channel.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
